BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 200.4 720 Td (Chapter 1: A Tiny Seed) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Once upon a time, there was a tiny seed named Seedling.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (She was no bigger than a pea, buried in the dark, cool earth.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('It is so dark down here,' Seedling whispered. 'When will I grow?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (A wise old worm crawled by. 'Be patient, little one. Your time will come.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('Inside you is everything you need to become something amazing!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (Seedling did not know it yet, but she was going to become a mighty oak tree!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: INSIDE A SEED) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (A seed is like a tiny suitcase packed with everything a plant needs to start life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (The seed coat is a tough outer shell that protects the baby plant inside.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Inside is an embryo - a tiny baby plant with a root, stem, and leaves already formed!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Seeds also carry stored food \(endosperm\) to feed the baby plant until it can make its own.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Seeds can wait dormant for years, even centuries, until conditions are just right!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* The world's oldest germinated seed was 2,000 years old \(a date palm from Israel\)!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* The biggest seed in the world is the coco de mer - it can weigh 40 pounds!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* A single sunflower head can contain up to 2,000 seeds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Soak a bean seed overnight, then carefully open it. Can you see the tiny baby plant inside?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (How do seeds 'know' when it is the right time to start growing?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
