BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 133.20000000000002 720 Td (Chapter 4: Making Food from Sunlight) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Seedling's leaves grew bigger and greener every day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td ('I am making my own food!' she announced proudly to the worm.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('How?' asked the worm. 'You do not have a mouth or a kitchen!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('I use sunlight, water from my roots, and air from the sky!' Seedling explained.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td ('My green leaves mix them all together to make sugar - my favorite food!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('And the best part? I breathe out oxygen that animals need to live!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: PHOTOSYNTHESIS) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Photosynthesis is how plants make food from sunlight \(photo=light, synthesis=making\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (The recipe: Sunlight + Water + Carbon Dioxide = Sugar + Oxygen.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Chlorophyll is the green chemical in leaves that captures sunlight energy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Plants take in CO2 \(carbon dioxide\) from the air through tiny holes in their leaves.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (They release oxygen \(O2\) as a waste product - which is what all animals breathe!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* One large tree produces enough oxygen for two people to breathe all year!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Leaves are green because chlorophyll reflects green light but absorbs red and blue.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* Photosynthesis produces all the oxygen in Earth's atmosphere!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Put a water plant \(like Elodea\) in water in sunlight. Watch oxygen bubbles form on the leaves!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (If plants make oxygen and we make carbon dioxide, how do we help each other?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
