BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 172.08 720 Td (ACTIVITY: LABEL THE PLANT PARTS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 72 680 Td (Draw a plant and label these parts:) Tj ET
